						<h3>Find relevant information about venues</h3>
						<br>
					  <p class="text-justify">
							People are always trying to find a cool restaurant with a great atmosphere
							to eat at or a popular bar or club where they will spend a memorable night.
							You could use one of the existing location-search apps that already exist.
							However, these apps use their own media database and their own rating system,
							which results in being forced to choose a place based on photos and ratings
							that are sometimes years old!
						</p>
						<br>
						<p class="text-justify">
								Happnin solves this problem. Instead of out-of-date venue information,
							you instead get a feed from some of the most popular social medias, Twitter
							and Instagram, that are cross-referenced with place data to show you
							what is actually happening <b>right now</b> at popular places around you.
							A surprise concert is taking place at a bar? People will surely be tweeting
							about that, and you won't miss out! On top of that, we built our own buzzmeter:
							rate the place on how the atmosphere currently is, and your rating will disappear
							when it becomes outdated. This ensures you're getting the most up-to-date
							information possible.
						</p>
						<br>
					  <p>You can easily find informations about:</p>
					  <ul>
							<li>Restaurants</li>
							<li>Cafes</li>
							<li>Clubs</li>
							<li>Bars</li>
					  </ul>
					</div>
			  </div><!-- .row -->

			  <br>
