					<div class="col-sm-6" >
						<br>
						<h3>How do you use it?</h3>
						<br>
						<p class="text-justify">
							Use Happnin when you want to find something to do or somewhere to go.
							Simply pull up the app, and you are presented with a list of restaurants,
							cafes, clubs, or bars around you (with the help of Yelp!). From there,
							simply select a venue to see a live feed of tweets and Instagram posts
							from that place! We also give you the ability to get directions to go there
							or call the place to make a quick reservation.
						</p>
						<br>
						<p class="text-justify">
							But what if you are planning to spend the evening in another city or
							part of town? Don't worry, Happnin has you covered! You can actually use
							Happnin to look up places in any city in the world. <i>How neat is
							that?</i>
						</p>
					</div>
