				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-sm-12">
						<p class="text-justify">
							The whole experience is based on a clever use of the available APIs.
							What's happnin' behind the scenes for every request is the following:
							<ul>
								<li>We retrieve your current location or the location you are
								searching plus the type of venues you are looking for and send it
								to our server.</li>
								<li>From there, we get a list of relevant places from Yelp!.</li>
								<li>We add our own information, including featured venues, on top of those from Yelp!.</li>
								<li>Once you've chosen a place, we get the most recent geo-tagged
									tweets and Instagram posts from that place.</li>
							</ul>
						</p>
						<br>
